moves left).. You can undo your mistakes, and relive the days of your youth. But once you go back, you can never reach that same path/position as before...</p>\n<p>You are what you are right now as an end product of all your good and bad times...</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a260e387a409ddf2730a53113518fd18/43142/different_path.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Different Path\"\n        title=\"Different Path\"\n        src=\"/static/a260e387a409ddf2730a53113518fd18/fcda8/different_path.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a260e387a409ddf2730a53113518fd18/12f09/different_path.png 148w,\n/static/a260e387a409ddf2730a53113518fd18/e4a3f/different_path.png 295w,\n/static/a260e387a409ddf2730a53113518fd18/fcda8/different_path.png 590w,\n/static/a260e387a409ddf2730a53113518fd18/43142/different_path.png 599w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<hr>\n<p>I wanted to create this as a large installation in some gallery...</p>\n<p>Some day...</p>\n<hr>\n<p><u><strong>PS(11th March 2021)</strong></u> : <br>\nNow that I look back at this old sketch, There are some things that I would like to change : </p>\n<ul>\n<li>The slider isn't that intuitive. Maybe adding a few markings would help.</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"The Path of Life","aut